{"title":"房屋擁有真實成本計算器","description":"計算擁有房屋的真實成本——30年內的按揭貸款、稅費、保險、HOA費用和維護費用。","url":"https://urcity.com/zh-tw/tools/home-ownership-calculator/","content":"\u003ch2 id=\"房屋擁有真實成本計算器\"\u003e房屋擁有真實成本計算器\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e買房不僅僅是按揭貸款。使用我們的房屋擁有真實成本計算器瞭解全貌。\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"calculator-widget\" id=\"home-calc\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-header\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"calc-icon green\"\u003e\n            \u003csvg\n                width=\"28\"\n                height=\"28\"\n                viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n                fill=\"none\"\n                stroke=\"currentColor\"\n                stroke-width=\"2\"\n            \u003e\n                \u003cpath d=\"M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\" /\u003e\n                \u003cpolyline points=\"9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22\" /\u003e\n            \u003c/svg\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"calc-title-group\"\u003e\n            \u003ch3\u003e房屋擁有真實成本計算器\u003c/h3\u003e\n            \u003cp class=\"calc-subtitle\"\u003e\n                瞭解30年內您實際需要支付的費用\n            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-inputs-row three-col\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n            \u003clabel for=\"home-price\"\u003e\n                \u003csvg\n                    width=\"16\"\n                    height=\"16\"\n                    viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n                    fill=\"none\"\n                    stroke=\"currentColor\"\n                    stroke-width=\"2\"\n                \u003e\n                    \u003cline x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\" /\u003e\n                    \u003cpath\n                        d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"\n                    /\u003e\n                \u003c/svg\u003e\n                房價\n            \u003c/label\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"input-prefix\"\u003e\n                \u003cspan class=\"prefix\"\u003e$\u003c/span\u003e\n                \u003cinput\n                    type=\"number\"\n                    id=\"home-price\"\n                    value=\"450000\"\n                    min=\"0\"\n                    step=\"10000\"\n                /\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n            \u003clabel for=\"down-payment\"\u003e\n                \u003csvg\n                    width=\"16\"\n                    height=\"16\"\n                    viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n                    fill=\"none\"\n                    stroke=\"currentColor\"\n                    stroke-width=\"2\"\n                \u003e\n                    \u003cpolyline points=\"23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18\" /\u003e\n                    \u003cpolyline points=\"17 6 23 6 23 12\" /\u003e\n                \u003c/svg\u003e\n                首付\n            \u003c/label\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"input-suffix\"\u003e\n                \u003cinput\n                    type=\"number\"\n                    id=\"down-payment\"\n                    value=\"20\"\n                    min=\"0\"\n                    max=\"100\"\n                    step=\"5\"\n                /\u003e\n                \u003cspan class=\"suffix\"\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"field-hint\" id=\"down-payment-hint\"\u003e\n                $90,000 首付\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n            \u003clabel for=\"interest-rate\"\u003e\n                \u003csvg\n                    width=\"16\"\n                    height=\"16\"\n                    viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n                    fill=\"none\"\n                    stroke=\"currentColor\"\n                    stroke-width=\"2\"\n                \u003e\n                    \u003cline x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\" /\u003e\n                    \u003cpath\n                        d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"\n                    /\u003e\n                \u003c/svg\u003e\n                利率\n            \u003c/label\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"input-suffix\"\u003e\n                \u003cinput\n                    type=\"number\"\n                    id=\"interest-rate\"\n                    value=\"6.5\"\n                    min=\"0\"\n                    max=\"20\"\n                    step=\"0.1\"\n                /\u003e\n                \u003cspan class=\"suffix\"\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-inputs-row three-col\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n            \u003clabel for=\"tax-rate\"\u003e\n                \u003csvg\n                    width=\"16\"\n                    height=\"16\"\n                    viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n                    fill=\"none\"\n                    stroke=\"currentColor\"\n                    stroke-width=\"2\"\n                \u003e\n                    \u003cpath\n                        d=\"M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z\"\n                    /\u003e\n                    \u003cpolyline points=\"14 2 14 8 20 8\" /\u003e\n                \u003c/svg\u003e\n                房產稅率\n            \u003c/label\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"input-suffix\"\u003e\n                \u003cinput\n                    type=\"number\"\n                    id=\"tax-rate\"\n                    value=\"1.8\"\n                    min=\"0\"\n                    max=\"5\"\n                    step=\"0.1\"\n                /\u003e\n                \u003cspan class=\"suffix\"\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n            \u003clabel for=\"hoa\"\u003e\n                \u003csvg\n                    width=\"16\"\n                    height=\"16\"\n                    viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n                    fill=\"none\"\n                    stroke=\"currentColor\"\n                    stroke-width=\"2\"\n                \u003e\n                    \u003crect x=\"2\" y=\"7\" width=\"20\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\" /\u003e\n                    \u003cpath d=\"M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16\" /\u003e\n                \u003c/svg\u003e\n                HOA月費\n            \u003c/label\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"input-prefix\"\u003e\n                \u003cspan class=\"prefix\"\u003e$\u003c/span\u003e\n                \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"hoa\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" step=\"50\" /\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-elec\" value=\"135\" /\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-water\" value=\"75\" /\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-net\" value=\"55\" /\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-trash\" value=\"30\" /\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-heating\" value=\"33\" /\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-cooling\" value=\"29\" /\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"util-currency\" value=\"USD\" /\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"calc-currency\" value=\"USD\" /\u003e\n\n    \u003cbutton class=\"btn btn-primary btn-large\" onclick=\"calculateHome()\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg\n            width=\"18\"\n            height=\"18\"\n            viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n            fill=\"none\"\n            stroke=\"currentColor\"\n            stroke-width=\"2\"\n        \u003e\n            \u003cpolyline points=\"22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/svg\u003e\n        計算總成本\n    \u003c/button\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-result\" id=\"home-result\" style=\"display: none\"\u003e\n        \n        \u003cdiv